      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". Elihu views the wicked man as almost certainly an oppressor, whose misdeeds \"cause the cry of the poor to come before God,\" and provoke God, the Avenger of the poor and needy, to visit him with chastisement. ",
